## 📊 SCHEMA / DATA MODEL (Current)

### Collections/Tables

```
[TABLE_1]/{id}
├── field_name (type)
├── field_name (type)
├── relationship: [TABLE_2]/{id}
└── timestamps: createdAt, updatedAt

[TABLE_2]/{id}
├── field_name (type)
├── nested_array[]
├── enum_field: ['value1', 'value2', 'value3']
└── metadata

[TABLE_3]/{id}
├── foreign_key: [TABLE_1]/{id}
├── status (active|inactive|pending)
└── data
```

**Key relationships:**
- [TABLE_1] ←→ [TABLE_2]: [1:many / many:many]
- [TABLE_3] depends on [TABLE_1]: [relationship type]

